thread.title: Dennis+T
thread.title_full: Auto Europe Canada reviewed by Dennis+T

author: Dennis+T
title: Dennis+T
text: Booking this car in advance was almost too simple. Even finding this website was simple. Everything to book the car is done on one page, no links....and they take AMEX (not a given anymore) so the cc company covers my collision rider (at a $9/day saving over 15 days). I've got better things to do with $145.
